Package efiscen_tools.gis.core

Contains main class and classes for core calculations.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Application
    Contains main application logic.
    Configuration
    This class is used to store configurations read from configuration file.
    Debugger
    Contains methods to debug share and result data.
    EfiscenToolsCLI
    Starts the main application class in command line
    Processor
    Class responsible for calculating species shares and results.
    RasterCompressor
    Class to create compressed versions of rasters.
    RasterCompressor.CompressedRasterFloat
    Compressed raster containing float values.
    RasterCompressor.CompressedRasterInt
    Compressed raster containing integer values.
    SpeciesMapping
    Represents a single link between a species in EFISCEN results and a species map.

Package efiscen_tools.gis.core Description

Contains main class and classes for core calculations. This package contains the main class of the program (EfiscenToolsCLI.java).
